     • Added self._cached_available_blocks and return cached result on subsequent calls.
  2) Made init_device idempotent via self._device_initialized guard.
  3) Made init_distributed_environment idempotent via self._dist_env_initialized and torch.distributed.is_initialized checks (avoids redundant setup).
  4) Micro-optimization: directly return LocalOrDistributedWorkerBase.execute_model(...) to skip a temporary variable.
  5) Ensured num_gpu_blocks aligns with scheduler behavior (+1) and assertion matches.
